Mechanic- (5)
- The mechanic can craft things to use in game.
- They can craft a turret, which gives them 2 weak attacks at any time they like. (takes 2 days (4 phases) to craft)
- They can craft a missile, which can strong attack 1 person. (Takes 3 days (6 phases) to craft) 
- The mechanic will lose all crafted items if they die, but won't lose crafting progress. 
- Using attacks are an night end visiting action.
- Respawns in 6 phases.
